OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1774598700
OL,3,CNHS doctor from South Gloucestershire
OL,4,Ccharged with inviting support for Hamas
OL,6,FAn NHS doctor from South
OL,7,FGloucestershire has been charged with
OL,8,Ffour counts of inviting support for
OL,9,FHamas, the Metropolitan Police has
OL,10,Fconfirmed.
OL,12,FDr Rahmeh Aladwan, 31, was arrested by
OL,13,Fofficers at her home address in
OL,14,FPilning on Thursday 26 March for
OL,15,Fallegedly breaching police bail
OL,16,Fconditions imposed following previous
OL,17,Farrests.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
