FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1774598700
OL,3,CNHS doctor from South Gloucestershire
OL,4,Ccharged with inviting support for Hamas
OL,6,FShe was then taken to a central London
OL,7,Fpolice station where she was charged
OL,8,Fwith four counts of inviting support
OL,9,Ffor Hamas, a proscribed group, in
OL,10,Fbreach of the Terrorism Act 2000.
OL,12,FThe charges date from July 23 to
OL,13,FDecember 31 2025.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1774598700
OL,3,CNHS doctor from South Gloucestershire
OL,4,Ccharged with inviting support for Hamas
OL,6,FShe was also charged with publishing
OL,7,For distributing written material, and
OL,8,Fusing words that were threatening,
OL,9,Fabusive or insulting, intending
OL,10,Fthereby to stir up racial hatred or
OL,11,Fhaving regard to all the circumstances
OL,12,Fwas reckless as to whether racial
OL,13,Fhatred would be stirred up, in breach
OL,14,Fof the Public Order Act 1986.
OL,16,FAladwan, who is British Palestinian,
OL,17,Fwas remanded in custody and will
OL,18,Fappear at Westminster Magistrates'
OL,19,FCourt on Friday, Scotland Yard said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/3
